# Model files (keep configurations but ignore large serialized weights except registry template)
# Actually in ML projects it's standard to exclude heavy serialized models,
# but we can let them be saved locally. We ignore all .joblib files under models/
# but keep models/.gitkeep or keep models directory structure.
models/*.joblib
!models/model_latest.joblib  # Keep latest for fast startup if needed, or ignore all
models/model_*.joblib
models/metadata_*.json
!models/metadata_latest.json # Keep latest metadata

